{"text_id":194115,"tokens":["Mid","latitude"," Cir","rus"," Clouds"," and"," Multiple"," Tro","po","pa","uses",":"," A"," ","2","0","0","2","-","2","0","0","6"," Cli","matology"," over"," the"," SIR","TA"," Observatory","\""," presents"," a"," comprehensive"," study"," of"," mid","latitude"," cir","rus"," clouds"," and"," multiple"," tropo","pa","uses"," observed"," at"," the"," SIR","TA"," observatory"," in"," France","."," The"," research"," aims"," to"," enhance"," the"," understanding"," of"," the"," relationship"," between"," these"," two"," phenomena"," and"," their"," impact"," on"," weather"," and"," climate",".","\n\n","Our"," methodology"," involved"," the"," use"," of"," ground","-","based"," lidar"," and"," ceil","ometer"," measurements",","," satellite"," data",","," and"," radio","son","de"," profiles"," to"," analyze"," the"," occurrence",","," properties",","," and"," structures"," of"," cir","rus"," clouds"," and"," multiple"," tropo","pa","uses","."," We"," also"," utilized"," a"," combination"," of"," statistical"," and"," atmospheric"," models"," to"," investigate"," the"," underlying"," processes"," and"," mechanisms"," responsible"," for"," their"," formation"," and"," interactions",".","\n\n","The"," study"," revealed"," that"," multiple"," tropo","pa","uses"," and"," cir","rus"," clouds"," frequently"," co","-","occur","red",","," with"," the"," former"," exhibiting"," a"," greater"," frequency"," during"," winter"," and"," the"," latter"," during"," summer","."," The"," results"," showed"," that"," mid","latitude"," cir","rus"," clouds"," were"," mostly"," associated"," with"," the"," upper"," tropo","pause",","," while"," their"," base"," could"," reach"," down"," to"," the"," lower"," tropo","pause"," or"," even"," the"," boundary"," layer","."," Moreover",","," the"," research"," highlighted"," the"," importance"," of"," multiple"," tropo","pa","uses"," as"," a"," crucial"," factor"," influencing"," cir","rus"," cloud"," properties",",","